  <brief_title>Optimization of EKG Method for Long Term Central Venous Catheter Tip Placement</brief_title>
  <official_title>P-max or P-submax? This is the Question! A Prospective Randomized Search of the Most Reliable ECG Landmark for a Long Term Central Venous Catheter.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
